{
  "keyword": "CRTOUTQ",
  "description": "Create Output Queue (CRTOUTQ)",
  "parameters": [
    {
      "name": "OUTQ",
      "description": "Output queue",
      "help": "Output queue (OUTQ)\n\nSpecifies the output queue being created.\n\nThis is a required parameter.\n\nQualifier 1: Output queue\n\nQualifier 2: Library\n\nNote: The temporary library QTEMP is not a valid library name. Output queues must be in permanent libraries.",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": true,
      "groupKind": "qualified",
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "LIB",
          "description": "Library",
          "help": "指定できる特殊値: *CURLIB",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false,
          "defaultValue": "*CURLIB",
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "OUTQ",
          "description": "Output queue",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": true,
          "attributes": {
            "characterSet": "upper",
            "maxLength": 10
          }
        }
      ],
      "positional": 1,
      "basic": true
    },
    {
      "name": "MAXPAGES",
      "description": "Maximum spooled file size",
      "help": "Maximum spooled file size (MAXPAGES)\n\nSpecifies the maximum spooled file size in pages that will be allowed to print between a starting and ending time. If a spooled file exceeds the page limit it will be deferred (DFR status) until the ending time expires. For files where the exact number of pages is not known, the estimated number of pages is used. (You can use the Work with Spooled File Attributes (WRKSPLFA) command to find out the estimated number of pages.) Time must be specified in hhmmss format, on a 24 hour clock.\n\nSingle values\n\nOther values (up to 5 repetitions)\n\nElement 1: Number of pages\n\nElement 2: Starting time\n\nElement 3: Ending time",
      "inputType": "group",
      "required": false,
      "groupKind": "elements",
      "singleValues": [
        "*NONE"
      ],
      "children": [
        {
          "name": "MAXPAGES_E1",
          "description": "Number of pages",
          "inputType": "number",
          "required": false,
          "attributes": {
            "numericOnly": true
          },
          "defaultValue": "*NONE"
        },
        {
          "name": "MAXPAGES_E2",
          "description": "Starting time",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false
        },
        {
          "name": "MAXPAGES_E3",
          "description": "Ending time",
          "inputType": "text",
          "required": false
        }
      ],
      "maxOccurrences": 5,
      "basic": true
    },
    {
      "name": "SEQ",
      "description": "Order of files on queue",
      "help": "Order of files on queue (SEQ)\n\nSpecifies the order of the spooled files on the output queue.",
      "inputType": "dropdown",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*FIFO",
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper"
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "*FIFO",
          "value": "*FIFO"
        },
        {
          "label": "*JOBNBR",
          "value": "*JOBNBR"
        }
      ],
      "basic": true
    },
    {
      "name": "RMTSYS",
      "description": "Remote system",
      "help": "Remote system (RMTSYS)\n\nSpecifies the remote system to send files to when a remote writer is started (using the STRRMTWTR command) to the output queue. This is referred to as the \"address\" by SNADS, and the \"host\" by TCP/IP.\n\nNote: This value is valid only when *IP has been specified for the CNNTYPE parameter.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *INTNETADR, *NONE, *PASTHR, *NWSA",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*NONE",
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper"
      },
      "basic": true
    },
    {
      "name": "RMTPRTQ",
      "description": "Remote printer queue",
      "help": "Remote printer queue (RMTPRTQ)\n\nSpecifies the printer queue on the remote system (RMTSYS parameter) to which the remote writer sends spooled files.\n\nNote: This value is valid only when the connection type (CNNTYPE parameter) is specified as *SNA or *USRDFN and the DESTTYPE is *OS400 or *S390.\n\nIf the name of the remote system needs to be lower case, the name must be enclosed in apostrophes. If you do not use apostrophes, the operating system changes the name to upper case.\n\nFor a destination system that is not an IBM System i, this name is system-dependent, and can be either the actual name of the device or the name of a printer queue.\n\nThis output queue is usually specified as library name/output queue name. If a library name qualifier is not specified, the value *LIBL is used as the default.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *USER, *SYSTEM",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*USER",
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper"
      },
      "promptControl": [
        {
          "controlParameter": "RMTSYS",
          "countRelation": "EQ",
          "count": 1,
          "conditions": [
            {
              "relation": "NE",
              "compareValue": "*NONE"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "AUTOSTRWTR",
      "description": "Writers to autostart",
      "help": "Writers to autostart (AUTOSTRWTR)\n\nSpecifies the number of remote writers that will be started automatically by the system. For user created output queues with the remote system (RMTSYS parameter) specified as *NONE, this parameter will be ignored.\n\n指定できる特殊値: *NONE",
      "inputType": "text",
      "required": false,
      "defaultValue": "*NONE",
      "attributes": {
        "characterSet": "upper"
      },
      "promptControl": [
        {
          "controlParameter": "RMTSYS",
          "countRelation": "EQ",
          "count": 1,
          "conditions": [
            {
              "relation": "NE",
              "compareValue": "*NONE"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "MSGQ",
      "description": "Queue for writer messages",
      "help": "Queue for writer messages (MSGQ)\n\nSpecifies the message queue to which messages are sent when created by the remote writer started to this output queue.\n\nQualifier 1: Queue for writer messages\n\nQualifier 2: Library",
